title: Person of Interest - I'll tell you the truth Fusco (05x09)
author: POI - Best Of
comment: the scene under the bridge when they all came together. BEAUTIFUL!
Who knew this  would be the last happy scene of POI :(
When I saw that Fusco's square was yellow, I was shedding a tear... :'-)
I really wanted to hear what Reese said to Fosco, I waited 5 years for it!, oh well.
So satisfying to finally see Fusco with a yellow box!
